snippet.textDisplay:
"Pea before you go."
Well that's just good practice in general. It's also good practice to top off your tank before you undertake a road trip, because who knows how long you'll be driving until you come across another gas station. Now you might think I give this advice lightly, but I've fallen victim to this one.
